public abstract class WFPTestSimulationFactory
extends java.lang.Object

The base class to create tests for Workflow patterns. Since the checking needs to be automated, the models defined in the tests must adhere to the following restrictions: - The simulation must be restricted to 1 day - Simulation Time Unit must be MINUTE - All the model objects (resources, resource types, activities, element types) defined must have consecutive identifiers starting in 0. There can not be missing indexes. - No random number generators should be used. - Resources must use a simple periodic cycle - The preferred cycle is the TableCycle

Author:
Iván Castilla Rodríguez
